name: Eunomia
description: Digital collage (4645x6193px) Eunomia - named after Eunomia, one of the Horae (Hours), a personification of order and law in Greek mythology.Eunomia is a very large asteroid in the inner asteroid belt. It is the largest of the stony (S-type) asteroids, and somewhere between the 8th- and 12th-largest main-belt asteroid overall
